06:54.860 --> 07:05.880
it with you and he took with him all of his wine and he had all the thousands of
bottles of wine in his cellar poured into his grave well Well, it was such a

07:05.880 --> 07:17.240
great idea that I wrote it as a short story last week and sent it off, and it'll
probably be in Playboy sometime in the next few, four, five months. Yeah, good.

